functions.remarks:
Use `WithPersistence` to adjust Redis persistence configuration, e.g.:
```
var cache = builder.AddRedis("cache")
.WithDataBindMount("myredisdata")
.WithPersistence(TimeSpan.FromSeconds(10), 5);
```

Use `WithPersistence` to adjust Redis persistence configuration, e.g.:
```
var cache = builder.AddRedis("cache")
.WithDataVolume()
.WithPersistence(TimeSpan.FromSeconds(10), 5);
```

